Indicate the date from which the detailed aging is enabled: For instance, if data are migrated from other systems and information is not completely avaliable, you can start seeing info from the date indicated.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000537-0/13AdvancedCustomerVendorStatement-en.png"><br>

The fields marked with "Report ID" refer to the reports to be executed for the different types.

Custom reports can be set, otherwise, if the fields are left blank, the system uses standard BC reports.